{"tid":1796553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曱甴王鄧小強係咪嫌無警時分玩唔夠，想玩無警月分？","createTime":"2019-12-24T16:40:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T08:08:07.000Z","uid":61282,"like":344,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"7128f76ce7d17ff3a74f32cb403dc415de26763d","tid":1796553,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:40:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他主動提及香港罪案數字上升，指是自6月起暴徒破壞香港，令罪案急升，又批評市民守法意識薄弱縱容罪行，令劫匪都開始「打爛舖頭」，使爆竊案及行劫案上升。<br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1069522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1069522&d=nB3K3ojK8rN8kNU4dsXAY77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=ec218807\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1069522&h=37256632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1069522</a><br />\n<br />\n前排啲曱甴高層已經想帶風向講話「暴徒」鼓勵犯罪行為，可能會令更多嚴重罪行例如搶劫甚至強姦發生<br />\n<br />\n今日鄧小強又出嚟鳩噏，而且明顯係想賴手足搞到罪案率上升，絕對有理由懷疑佢係想重現721，仲要係長期版；透過破壞社會治安同製造混亂，令一啲立場唔堅定嘅人怪責示威者<br />\n<br />\n其實呢招就不嬲都玩緊，卧底狗自己落場裝修，政府熄交通燈扮爛，黨鐵閘機扮壞，但似乎鄧小強想再升級，放任罪案發生（甚至黑警自己落手），然後夾硬賴係示威者搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果打劫金舖、錶舖冇用，話唔定會轉向平民落手，甚至強姦，大家睇路"},{"pid":"e44668d125673855041307bb26dc46f0371861ad","tid":1796553,"uid":108016,"like":184,"dislike":1,"score":183,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:45:43.000Z","msg":"打劫嗰班係休班警嚟"},{"pid":"383d5a9d5efa05877567e2bf97e3a7f33b3c634d","tid":1796553,"uid":69646,"like":68,"dislike":6,"score":62,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:46:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5ed345a6b1d2565aa3ceff1d30e7e076029bc77","tid":1796553,"uid":124410,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e44668d125673855041307bb26dc46f0371861ad","tid":1796553,"uid":108016,"like":184,"dislike":1,"score":183,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:45:43.000Z","msg":"打劫嗰班係休班警嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:46:57.000Z","msg":"唔排除任何可能性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce72970dc2bd2dedb69f7d55559f39bda3fc169","tid":1796553,"uid":258696,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:47:05.000Z","msg":"化療式打壓示威"},{"pid":"ea09071c9e9f2c32ee3f4c0b7792e91c4b8d65bb","tid":1796553,"uid":187664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:47:31.000Z","msg":"攬炒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b88743aedf2c08275603b35040a0a9b09149bbe","tid":1796553,"uid":258696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"383d5a9d5efa05877567e2bf97e3a7f33b3c634d","tid":1796553,"uid":69646,"like":68,"dislike":6,"score":62,"quote":{"pid":"7128f76ce7d17ff3a74f32cb403dc415de26763d","tid":1796553,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:40:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他主動提及香港罪案數字上升，指是自6月起暴徒破壞香港，令罪案急升，又批評市民守法意識薄弱縱容罪行，令劫匪都開始「打爛舖頭」，使爆竊案及行劫案上升。<br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1069522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1069522&d=nB3K3ojK8rN8kNU4dsXAY77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=ec218807\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1069522&h=37256632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1069522</a><br />\n<br />\n前排啲曱甴高層已經想帶風向講話「暴徒」鼓勵犯罪行為，可能會令更多嚴重罪行例如搶劫甚至強姦發生<br />\n<br />\n今日鄧小強又出嚟鳩噏，而且明顯係想賴手足搞到罪案率上升，絕對有理由懷疑佢係想重現721，仲要係長期版；透過破壞社會治安同製造混亂，令一啲立場唔堅定嘅人怪責示威者<br />\n<br />\n其實呢招就不嬲都玩緊，卧底狗自己落場裝修，政府熄交通燈扮爛，黨鐵閘機扮壞，但似乎鄧小強想再升級，放任罪案發生（甚至黑警自己落手），然後夾硬賴係示威者搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果打劫金舖、錶舖冇用，話唔定會轉向平民落手，甚至強姦，大家睇路"},"citedBy":3,"rep