f33b3c634d","tid":1796553,"uid":69646,"like":68,"dislike":6,"score":62,"quote":{"pid":"7128f76ce7d17ff3a74f32cb403dc415de26763d","tid":1796553,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:40:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他主動提及香港罪案數字上升，指是自6月起暴徒破壞香港，令罪案急升，又批評市民守法意識薄弱縱容罪行，令劫匪都開始「打爛舖頭」，使爆竊案及行劫案上升。<br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1069522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1069522&d=nB3K3ojK8rN8kNU4dsXAY77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=ec218807\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1069522&h=37256632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1069522</a><br />\n<br />\n前排啲曱甴高層已經想帶風向講話「暴徒」鼓勵犯罪行為，可能會令更多嚴重罪行例如搶劫甚至強姦發生<br />\n<br />\n今日鄧小強又出嚟鳩噏，而且明顯係想賴手足搞到罪案率上升，絕對有理由懷疑佢係想重現721，仲要係長期版；透過破壞社會治安同製造混亂，令一啲立場唔堅定嘅人怪責示威者<br />\n<br />\n其實呢招就不嬲都玩緊，卧底狗自己落場裝修，政府熄交通燈扮爛，黨鐵閘機扮壞，但似乎鄧小強想再升級，放任罪案發生（甚至黑警自己落手），然後夾硬賴係示威者搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果打劫金舖、錶舖冇用，話唔定會轉向平民落手，甚至強姦，大家睇路"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:46:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T07:27:14.000Z","msg":"喱樣真<br />\n出面好危險 返屋企保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598fd2142e22fb266c1214333ef9231c900418ab","tid":1796553,"uid":142735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T07:31:50.000Z","msg":"罪案急升即係表示警方唔做野<br />\n真係咩野都可以賴落示威者身上"},{"pid":"3a1288d4cabb8811326391b32c6d04ab3fe82ebf","tid":1796553,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34abf3b2c8afd48f379de481dfbc7bc79ad888fb","tid":1796553,"uid":69646,"like":0,"dislike":